---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="404 | Página no encontrada">
  <div class="error-container">
    <div class="error-content" data-aos="fade-up">
      <div class="image-wrapper">
        <img src="/images/Robot.png" alt="Robot Nova" class="floating-robot" />
        <div class="error-code">404</div>
      </div>
      
      <h1>¡Ups! Parece que nos <span>perdimos</span></h1>
      <p>Nova buscó por todo el sistema, pero no pudo encontrar la página que estás buscando. Puede que la dirección sea incorrecta o haya sido movida.</p>
      
      <div class="actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Volver al inicio</a>
        <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="history.back()">Regresar atrás</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .error-container {
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .error-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    width: 90%;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .floating-robot {
    width: 180px;
    height: auto;
    animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .error-code {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10px;
    right: -20px;
    font-size: 5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.1);
    line-height: 1;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  h1 span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-blue), var(--color-primary-green));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-medium);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-primary-green);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #12ad33;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.4);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: #f1f5f9;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: #e2e8f0;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(5deg); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .error-content {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    .actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .floating-robot {
      width: 140px;
    }
  }
</style>
